peloton/
This source tree is the root of the core Python Peloton code

install/
This source tree contains code for installation tools for our supported
target distributions:

 * Debian
 * Ubuntu
 * Gentoo
 * Redhat/CentOS
 * Python Easy Install (Egg)

services/
Core services that we may wish to distribute as part of the default Peloton
package. No non-core services should be placed in this location.

tools/
Tools for running, monitoring and managing Peloton clusters.
